'''颶風伊塞萊'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Iselle}}），也譯作'''颶風依莎娜'''<ref>{{cite news|author=周琪|url=https://www.ntdtv.com/gb/2014/08/08/a1128902.html|title=22年首次 飓风依莎娜登陆夏威夷|publisher=新唐人電視台|date=2014-08-08|accessdate=2014-08-09|archive-date=2021-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210402113915/https://www.ntdtv.com/gb/2014/08/08/a1128902.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是有歷史記錄以來[[登陸_(氣象學)|登陸]][[夏威夷島|夏威夷大島]]最強的[[熱帶氣旋|熱帶氣旋]]。[[2014年太平洋颶風季|2014年太平洋颶風季]]的第十一個[[熱帶氣旋命名|被命名]]的風暴，伊塞萊在2014年7月31日於[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]西南方的一片不穏定天氣的地區{{link-en|熱帶氣旋發展學|Tropical cyclogenesis|發展}}。假設氣旋在其存在的時間保持一個西北偏西的路線，大致有利的大氣條件允許其逐漸增強，氣旋在形成後一天達到颶風狀態。氣旋在接下來數天繼續增強，直到8月4日，當伊塞萊達到[[最大持續風速|最大持續風速]]為每小時220公里，最低[[氣壓|氣壓]]為947[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]；27.96[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高強度，這使其成為[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级#分級|四級颶風]]。此後，伊塞萊遇到了惡劣的環境條件，並迅速減弱，期後在8月8日以中等熱帶風暴的強度登陸大島。氣旋通過島嶼期間受到干擾，伊塞萊後來在8月9日消散。

早在8月2日，因為預計風暴有可能在夏威夷登陸，所以夏威夷居民普遍採取了預防措施。時任州長[[尼尔·阿伯克龙比|尼尔·阿伯克龙比]]簽署了緊急公告，許多政府設施關閉。數間航空公司取消了為該群島提供服務的航班。登陸時，伊塞萊帶來暴雨和造成強風，導致大量[[停電|停電]]和樹木倒塌。風暴造成重大的農作物損失，估計為7920萬（2014年[[美元|美元]]），包括該州失去60%的[[番木瓜|番木瓜]]。這足以被歸類為農業災難，最初被[[聯邦緊急事務管理署|聯邦緊急事務管理署]]否認，但期後該管理署宣佈此為災難。由於水災，風暴也在[[考艾岛|考艾岛]]造成一人死亡。

==氣象歷史==
{{Storm path|Iselle 2014 track.png|size=250px}}
2014年7月下旬，[[數值天氣預報|電腦模型]]開始顯示[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]西南沿海地區可能有[[低气压|低氣壓區]]形成，促使[[國家颶風中心|國家颶風中心]]在7月24日對該區的{{link-en|熱帶氣旋發展學|Tropical cyclogenesis|熱帶氣旋發展}}的概率評估為低<ref name=TWOEP201407241751>{{cite web|author1=Blake, Eric S.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=East Pacific Tropical Weather Outlook for 11:00 AM, PDT on July 24, 2014|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201407241751.txt|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|format=TXT|date=2014-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102807/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2014/TWOEP.201407241751.txt|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這些預測在7月28日開始實現，當時一股與[[东风波|东风波]]有關的[[雷暴|雷暴]]在墨西哥沿岸發展<ref>{{cite web|author1=Berg, Robbie J.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=East Pacific Tropical Weather Outlook for 5:00 PM, PDT on July 28, 2014|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201407282322&basin=epac&fdays=2|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|format=TXT|date=2014-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102626/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201407282322&basin=epac&fdays=2|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在有利條件下向西移動，該系統在接下來的幾天內組織起來<ref>{{cite web|author1=Kimberlain, Todd B.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=East Pacific Tropical Weather Outlook for 5:00 PM, PDT on July 28, 2014|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201407300146&basin=epac&fdays=2|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|format=TXT|date=2014-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102829/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201407300146&basin=epac&fdays=2|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一熱帶低氣壓在{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}7月31日中午12時形成<ref name="TCR">{{cite report|author=Todd B. Kimberlain|publisher=National Hurricane Center|date=2015-01-29|accessdate=2017-05-22|title=Hurricane Iselle|series=Tropical Cyclone Report|url={{NHC TCR url|id=EP092014_Iselle}}|location=Miami, Florida|format=PDF}}</ref>。六小時後，基於系統的組織以及{{link-en|MetOp|MetOp|MetOp-B}}{{link-en|散射儀|Scatterometer}}探測到的熱帶風暴的風力，國家颶風中心將低氣壓升級為熱帶風暴伊塞萊<ref name=Disc1>{{cite web|author1=Berg, Robbie J.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=Tropical Storm Iselle Discussion Number 1|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.001.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102340/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.001.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TCR"/>。當時伊塞萊位於[[下加利福尼亞半島|下加利福尼亞半島]]最南端西南方約1,730公里<ref>{{cite web|author1=Berg, Robbie J.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=Tropical Storm Iselle Advisory Number 1|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.public.001.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102342/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.public.001.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。系統形成後穩定地增強，國家颶風中心指出風暴有[[快速增强|快速增强]]的可能性<ref>{{cite web|author1=Brennan, Michael J.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=Tropical Storm Iselle Discussion Number 2|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.002.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102822/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.002.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月1日，伊塞萊開始發展出[[風眼|風眼]]<ref>{{cite web|author1=Berg, Robbie J.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=Tropical Storm Iselle Discussion Number 6|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.004.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102828/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.004.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這種漸進的組織模式促使國家颶風中心在{{lang|en|UTC}}翌日凌晨0時將風暴升級至颶風標準<ref name="TCR"/>。

雖然有利的條件使伊塞萊在發展早期不受限制地增強<ref>{{cite web|author1=Blake, Eric S.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Discussion Number 7|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.007.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102639/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.007.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，中度[[风切变|风切变]]在8月2日對颶風造成短暫影響，阻止雷暴的加強並使風暴的垂直外形變得略微畸形<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite web|author1=Berg, Robbie|author2=National Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Discussion Number 9|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.008.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102637/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.008.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過，這些情況隨後很快就消失，允許伊塞萊在當天晚上恢復加強並達到二級颶風標準<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite web|author1=Berg, Robbie|author2=National Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Discussion Number 9|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.009.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102621/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.009.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨著風切變不再影響伊塞萊的組織，熱帶氣旋逐漸變得更加對稱<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite web|author1=Kimberlain, Todd B.|author2=National Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Discussion Number 10|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.010.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102710/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.010.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，使颶風曾經粗糙的風眼清除雲層覆蓋，風暴在8月3日加強至[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级|大型颶風]]標準<ref name=Disc11>{{cite web|author1=Berg, Robbie|author2=National Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Discussion Number 11|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.012.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102811/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.012.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。獲得一些[[環狀熱帶氣旋|環狀熱帶氣旋]]特徵，伊塞萊在{{lang|en|UTC}}8月4日中午12時達到{{link-en|四級太平洋颶風列表|List of Category 4 Pacific hurricanes|四級}}標準<ref name="TCR"/>。隨後伊塞萊在{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上6時達到[[最大持續風速|最大持續風速]]每小時220公里、最低氣壓947[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]；27.96[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高強度<ref name="TCR"/>。與此同時，颶風擁有一直徑45公里的風眼<ref>{{cite web|author1=Berg, Robbie J.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Discussion Number 18|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.018.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102820/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.018.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:Iselle_Aug_7_2014_2315Z_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]
達到最高強度後，受較強的風切變和較低的[[海面溫度|海面溫度]]兩方面影響，伊塞萊開始緩緩地減弱，風暴在8月5日早上跌至低於四級標準<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite web|author1=Stewart, Stacy R.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Discussion Number 20|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.020.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-04|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812102800/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.discus.020.shtml|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。持續的風切變導致風暴進一步衰退，其風眼外觀變得粗糙。當天{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上6時，國家颶風中心將伊塞萊降級至低於大型颶風標準<ref name="TCR"/>。{{lang|en|UTC}}8月6日凌晨0時，預報責任從國家颶風中心轉移到[[中太平洋颶風中心|中太平洋颶風中心]]<ref name="TCR"/>。雖然此後風切變開始減少，但是充足的乾空氣導致伊塞萊迅速減弱，在8月6日跌至一級標準<ref>{{cite web|author1=Houston, Sam|author2=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Discussion Number 25|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.025.1408061516|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-06|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812101454/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.025.1408061516|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，受抑制的風切變使颶風在靠近[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]期間能夠重新組織並保持一大型風眼<ref>{{cite web|author1=Houston, Sam|work=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Special Discussion Number 26|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.026.1408061710|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-06|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812101456/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.026.1408061710|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，伊塞萊在{{lang|en|UTC}}8月7日凌晨0時達到風力時速155公里的第二波最高強度<ref name="TCR"/>。8月7日，風暴北面的上層[[低壓槽|槽]]導致風切變增強，風暴的風眼消失，中太平洋颶風中心估計伊塞萊減弱至颶風的最低標準<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite web|author1=Ballard, Robert|work=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Discussion Number 31|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.031.1408072050|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-07|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810052401/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.031.1408072050|archive-date=2014-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。系統受強烈風切變破壞，伊塞萊在翌日減弱為熱帶風暴，隨後在{{lang|en|UTC}}中午12時30分以風力時速95公里在[[夏威夷島|大島]]的{{link-en|考烏|Kau, Hawaii}}海岸[[登陸_(氣象學)|登陸]]<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite web|author1=Birchard, Tom|work=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Tropical Storm Iselle Discussion Number 34|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.034.1408081501|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-08|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812104132/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.034.1408081501|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該島的山脈地形在很大程度上擾亂伊塞萊的主要氣旋環流，中太平洋颶風中心注意到夏威夷群島以南出現小[[漩渦|漩渦]]<ref>{{cite web|author1=Ballard, Robert|work=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Tropical Storm Iselle Discussion Number 35|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.035.1408082030|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-09|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810050811/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.035.1408082030|archive-date=2014-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於風暴中心不再有持續的雷暴活動，中太平洋颶風中心在8月9日決定將伊塞萊降級為殘留低氣壓區<ref>{{cite web|author1=Donaldson, Pete|work=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Post-Tropical Cyclone Iselle Discussion Number 37|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.037.1408090842|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-09|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812114848/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCDCP3.EP092014.037.1408090842|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當時，該擾動集結在[[檀香山|檀香山]]西南偏西約320公里<ref>{{cite web|author1=Donaldson, Pete|work=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Post-Tropical Cyclone Iselle Advisory Number 37|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/WEB_TCPCP3.EP092014.037.1408090830.php|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-09|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811050434/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/WEB_TCPCP3.EP092014.037.1408090830.php|archive-date=2014-08-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。伊塞萊的殘留低氣壓在兩天後消散<ref name="TCR" />。

==防災措施==
[[File:Iselle_Aug_8_2014_0600–2000Z_RBTOP_IR.gif|250px]]
{{lang|en|UTC}}8月5日晚上9時，中太平洋颶風中心為[[夏威夷島|夏威夷島]]發佈[[熱帶風暴觀察預警|熱帶風暴觀察預警]]<ref name=Fsct22>{{cite web|author1=Birchard, Tom|work=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Forecast/Advisory Number 22|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCMCP3.EP092014.022.1408052039|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-06|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809005818/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCMCP3.EP092014.022.1408052039|archive-date=2014-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>；早在8月2日，國家颶風中心發布的預測表明伊塞萊有在夏威夷群島上空或附近經過的可能性<ref name=Fcst10>{{cite web|author1=Kimberlain, Todd B.|work=National Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Forecast/Advisory Number 10|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.fstadv.010.shtml?|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-05|location=Miami, Florida|date=2014-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002190030/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2014/ep09/ep092014.fstadv.010.shtml|archive-date=2015-10-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨著颶風越來越靠近群島，觀察預警向西延伸至[[歐胡島|歐胡島]]<ref name=Fsct25>{{cite web|author1=Houston, Sam|work=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Forecast/Advisory Number 25|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCMCP3.EP092014.025.1408061430|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-06|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809004400/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCMCP3.EP092014.025.1408061430|archive-date=2014-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。與伊塞萊相關的首個[[颶風警告|颶風警告]]在8月6日向[[夏威夷縣|夏威夷縣]]發佈<ref name=HurricaneWarning>{{cite web|author1=Magin, Janis L.|title=Hurricane warning issued for Hawaii County as Iselle nears|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/pacific/blog/morning_call/2014/08/oahu-joins-maui-hawaii-counties-under-tropical.html|agency=American City Business Journals|publisher=Pacific Business News|date=2014-08-06|accessdate=2014-08-06|archive-date=2022-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220116120305/https://www.bizjournals.com/pacific/blog/morning_call/2014/08/oahu-joins-maui-hawaii-counties-under-tropical.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當晚，[[茂宜島|茂宜島]]、[[摩洛凱島|摩洛凱島]]、[[拉奈島|拉奈島]]、[[卡胡拉威島|卡胡拉威島]]和[[歐胡島|歐胡島]]接獲熱帶風暴警告<ref name=Fsct25 />。8月7日早上，熱帶風暴警告延伸至[[考艾岛|考艾岛]]，使所有[[夏威夷群島|夏威夷群島]]的主要島嶼均處於[[熱帶氣旋警告|熱帶氣旋警告]]之下<ref name=Fsct30>{{cite web|author1=Birchard, Tom|work=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Forecast/Advisory Number 30|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCMCP3.EP092014.030.1408071445|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-07|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812101508/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCMCP3.EP092014.030.1408071445|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。水災的可能性亦導致整個群島收到{{link-en|山洪暴發觀察預警|Flash flood watch}}<ref name=TSTFlood>{{cite news|title=Tropical storm, flash flood watches issued as Hurricane Iselle approaches|url=http://khon2.com/2014/08/03/hawaii-keeps-a-watchful-eye-on-hurricane-iselle/|accessdate=2014-08-06|agency=KHON2|publisher=LIN Television Corporation|date=2014-08-03|location=Honolulu, Hawaii}}</ref>。8月9日，隨着伊塞萊不再對這些島嶼構成威脅，所有警告均被解除<ref name=Fsct36>{{cite web|author1=Ballard, Robert|work=Central Pacific Hurricane Center|title=Hurricane Iselle Forecast/Advisory Number 30|url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCMCP3.EP092014.036.1408090248|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-08-09|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|date=2014-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812114652/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2014/TCMCP3.EP092014.036.1408090248|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於伊塞萊和[[2014年太平洋颶風季#颶風胡里奧（Julio）|颶風胡里奧]]均有可能帶來影響，夏威夷州州長[[尼尔·阿伯克龙比|尼尔·阿伯克龙比]]簽署緊急命令，從而為將來的救援和減災解行動分配資源<ref name=Emergency>{{cite news|title=Governor signs emergency proclamation in anticipation of tropical cyclones|url=http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26215528/governor-signs-emergency-proclamation-in-anticipation-of-tropical-cyclones|accessdate=2014-08-06|agency=HawaiiNewsNow|publisher=KHNL, WorldNow|date=2014-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808230627/http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26215528/governor-signs-emergency-proclamation-in-anticipation-of-tropical-cyclones|archive-date=2014-08-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。茂宜縣縣長{{link-en|艾倫·阿拉卡瓦|Alan Arakawa}}宣佈該縣進入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name=MauiSOE>{{cite news|title=Maui Mayor declares state of emergency for Maui County|url=http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26219434/maui-mayor-declares-state-of-emergency-for-maui-county|accessdate=2014-08-07|agency=HawaiiNewsNow|publisher=KHNL, WorldNow|date=2014-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114032606/http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26219434/maui-mayor-declares-state-of-emergency-for-maui-county|archive-date=2015-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於面臨風暴即將來臨的威脅，高度逼切感促使居民儲備必需品<ref name=HawaiiLoads>{{cite news|author1=Esser, Doug|author2=Garcia, Oskar|title=Hawaii loads up on supplies as 2 major storms loom|url=https://news.yahoo.com/hawaii-loads-supplies-2-major-storms-loom-203412228.html|accessdate=2014-08-06|agency=Associated Press|publisher=Yahoo News|date=2014-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114004827/http://news.yahoo.com/hawaii-loads-supplies-2-major-storms-loom-203412228.html|archive-date=2015-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然沒有計劃進行強制撤離，但夏威夷縣低窪地區的居民因[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]和水災威脅而被要求撤離<ref name=SheltersOpen />。沿海{{link-en|考烏|Kau, Hawaii}}和{{link-en|普納 (夏威夷州)|Puna, Hawaii|普納}}地區的居民收到建議採取預防措施，並在必要時撤離到高地<ref name=EffectsFelt>{{cite news|author1=Yager, Bret|title=Iselle effects felt on Big Island|url=http://westhawaiitoday.com/hurricane-season-2014/iselle-effects-felt-big-island|accessdate=2014-08-07|work=West Hawaii Today|agency=Stephens Media Hawaii|publisher=Stephens Media, LLC|date=2014-08-07|archive-date=2014-08-12|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140812041521/http://westhawaiitoday.com/hurricane-season-2014/iselle-effects-felt-big-island|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。由於預計一些海面的海浪將達到3至4.6米，[[美国海岸警卫队|美国海岸警卫队]]敦促船民和海員小心駕駛<ref name=toweaken>{{cite news|author1=Gima, Craig|title=Hurricanes to weaken, but still threaten Hawaii|url=http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/breaking/20140805_Iselle_weakens_slightly_as_2_storms_head_toward_Hawaii.html|accessdate=2014-08-06|newspaper=Honolulu Star Advertiser|date=2014-08-06|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808212800/http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/breaking/20140805_Iselle_weakens_slightly_as_2_storms_head_toward_Hawaii.html|archive-date=2014-08-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。海岸警衛隊還準備關閉部分夏威夷縣和茂宜縣的港口<ref name=PrepareShutdown>{{cite news|url=http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/breaking/20140806_Coast_Guard_preparing_to_shut_down_Hawaii_island_Maui_County_ports.html?id=270261001|title=Coast Guard preparing to shut down Hawaii island, Maui County ports|newspaper=Honolulu Star-Advertiser|accessdate=2014-08-07|date=2014-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814155549/http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/breaking/20140806_Coast_Guard_preparing_to_shut_down_Hawaii_island_Maui_County_ports.html?id=270261001|archive-date=2014-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[茂宜县|茂宜县]]，[[夏威夷州教育部|夏威夷州教育部]]下令關閉所有學校並開放一些設施作緊急避難所<ref name=MauiContinues>{{cite news|title=Maui Continues Preparations for Iselle’s Stormy Weather|url=http://mauinow.com/2014/08/05/maui-continues-preparations-for-iselles-stormy-weather/|accessdate=2014-08-06|publisher=Mauinow.com|date=2014-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808214435/http://mauinow.com/2014/08/05/maui-continues-preparations-for-iselles-stormy-weather/|archive-date=2014-08-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該部門亦關閉所有夏威夷縣的公立學校<ref name=MoreClosures>{{cite news|title=Big Island and Maui County schools canceled Thursday as Hurricane Iselle nears state|url=http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26207050/big-island-and-maui-county-schools-canceled-thursday-as-hurricane-iselle-nears-state|accessdate=2014-08-06|agency=HawaiiNewsNow|publisher=KHNL, WorldNow|date=2014-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807061601/http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26207050/big-island-and-maui-county-schools-canceled-thursday-as-hurricane-iselle-nears-state|archive-date=2014-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[夏威夷大学|夏威夷大学]]和{{link-en|夏威夷社區學院|Hawaii Community College}}均在伊塞萊來襲期間關閉他們的校園<ref name=SheltersOpen>{{cite news|author1=Callis, Tom|title=Shelters open, government agencies close ahead of Hurricane Iselle|url=http://westhawaiitoday.com/hurricane-season-2014/shelters-open-government-agencies-close-ahead-hurricane-iselle|accessdate=2014-08-07|work=West Hawaii Today|agency=Stephens Media Hawaii|publisher=Stephens Media, LLC|date=2014-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810104745/http://westhawaiitoday.com/hurricane-season-2014/shelters-open-government-agencies-close-ahead-hurricane-iselle|archive-date=2014-08-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。{{link-en|夏威夷土地及自然資源部|Hawai'i Department of Land and Natural Resources}}關閉夏威夷縣和茂宜縣的所有管理土地，並關閉了歐胡島和考艾島的一些露營地和荒野地區<ref name=DLNR>{{cite news|author1=Storms, Jade|title=DLNR to close areas for arrival of Iselle and Julio storm systems|url=http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26207580/dlnr-to-close-areas-for-arrival-of-iselle-and-julio-storm-systems|accessdate=2014-08-06|agency=HawaiiNewsNow|publisher=KHNL, WorldNow|date=2014-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810034751/http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26207580/dlnr-to-close-areas-for-arrival-of-iselle-and-julio-storm-systems|archive-date=2014-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。夏威夷縣的所有州辦事處和法院大樓均關閉，只保留必要的工作人員<ref name=SheltersOpen />。雖然[[夏威夷航空|夏威夷航空]]沒有取消其航班，但該航空豁免收取乘客在伊塞萊來襲期間更改航班的費用<ref name=HAirlines>{{cite news|author1=Ubay, Jason|title=Hawaiian Airlines to waive change fees due to Hurricane Iselle and Tropical Storm Julio|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/pacific/news/2014/08/05/hawaiian-airlines-to-waive-change-fees-due-to.html|accessdate=2014-08-06|agency=Pacific Business News|publisher=American City Business Journals|date=2014-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810014049/http://www.bizjournals.com/pacific/news/2014/08/05/hawaiian-airlines-to-waive-change-fees-due-to.html|archive-date=2014-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[聯合航空|聯合航空]]和[[海島航空|海島航空]]其後來採取相同的調節措施<ref name=SchoolsCloseResidentsStock>{{cite news|author1=Hanna, Josh|author2=Castillo, Mariano|author3=Hetter, Katia|author4=Marco, Tony|title=Schools close, residents stock up as Hawaii preps for rare cyclones|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/08/06/us/hawaii-storms/|accessdate=2014-08-06|agency=Cable News Network|publisher=Cable News Network|date=2014-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809215801/http://www.cnn.com/2014/08/06/us/hawaii-storms|archive-date=2014-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後者在8月7日取消所有夏威夷州的本地航班，但飛往[[考艾岛|考艾岛]]的航班除外<ref name=Cancel>{{cite news|author1=Kelleher, Jennifer Sinco|author2=McAvoy, Audrey|title=Hawaii airline cancels inter-island flights|url=https://news.yahoo.com/hawaii-airline-cancels-inter-island-flights-145058532.html|accessdate=2014-08-07|agency=Associated Press|publisher=Yahoo News|date=2014-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114004259/http://news.yahoo.com/hawaii-airline-cancels-inter-island-flights-145058532.html|archive-date=2015-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>；隨著伊塞萊的威脅越來越大，[[美國航空|美國航空]]和眾多其他航空也紛紛跟隨<ref name=SheltersOpen /><ref name=Moreairlines>{{cite news|author1=Kelleher, Jennifer Sinco|author2=McAvoy, Audrey|title=More airlines cancel Hawaii flights as storm looms|url=https://news.yahoo.com/more-airlines-cancel-hawaii-flights-storm-looms-001138833.html|accessdate=2014-08-08|agency=Associated Press|publisher=Yahoo News|date=2014-08-07|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114005633/http://news.yahoo.com/more-airlines-cancel-hawaii-flights-storm-looms-001138833.html|archive-date=2015-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[救世軍|救世軍]]為準備伊塞萊的救援行動，在夏威夷州準備資源<ref name=SheltersOpen />。

==影響==
伊塞萊經過時，除[[尼豪島|尼豪島]]外，該州的大部分地區均受熱帶風暴強度的風力影響，[[夏威夷群島|夏威夷群島]]其餘島嶼的陣風均超過每小時63公里。颶風度的風力確認在大島上的[[茂纳凯亚火山|茂纳凯亚火山]]出現，觀測到每小時146公里的陣風<ref>{{cite web|work=National Weather Service Office in Honolulu, Hawaii |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |date=2014-08-08 |accessdate=2014-08-10 |title=Iselle Brings Gusty Winds Across the State of Hawaii |url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/data/HFO/PNSHFO.1408090716 |archivedate=2014-08-10 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rj3rn85Q?url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/data/HFO/PNSHFO.1408090716 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。大部分南部島嶼受暴雨影響，大島某些地區的雨量由於伊塞萊背面南風的地形抬升而超過300毫米。最高總雨量出現在{{link-en|哈卡勞森林國家野生動物保護區|Hakalau Forest National Wildlife Refuge}}，觀察到387毫米的雨量。島嶼上{{link-en|向風面及背風面|Windward and leeward|背風面}}地區的降雨量明顯較少；在風暴經過時，[[科納國際機場|科納國際機場]]僅錄得1毫米的雨量。考艾島有數個地區的降雨量超過150毫米，[[美國地質調查局|美國地質調查局]]在基洛哈納山脊（{{lang|en|Kilohana Ridge}}）沿線的測站觀察到最大降雨量為243毫米。歐胡島北部最高點的總雨量為107毫米，而摩洛凱島和拉奈島僅錄得微量的雨量<ref>{{cite web|work=National Weather Service Office in Honolulu, Hawaii |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |date=2014-08-10 |accessdate=2014-08-10 |title=Iselle Brought Heavy Rainfall and Flooding to Hawaii |url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/data/HFO/PNSHFO.1408092020 |archivedate=2014-08-10 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Rj2pLvMT?url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/data/HFO/PNSHFO.1408092020 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。來自颶風伊塞萊和胡里奧的湧浪亦在夏威夷群島東岸產生出1.8至3米的海浪<ref name="ncdc"/>。

[[File:Iselle_radar_20140808_0845_UTC.png|thumb]]
伊塞萊在大島的東岸帶來具破壞性的衝浪。強風將[[希洛_(夏威夷州)|希洛]]附近的房屋屋頂呚開，並使樹木倒塌<ref name=IselleLandfall>{{cite news|author1=Bagley, Andrea|title=iselle makes landfall, power outages and flooding reported|url=http://www.theweathernetwork.com/news/articles/iselle-makes-landfall-power-outages-and-flooding-reported/33639|accessdate=2014-08-08|publisher=The Weather Network|date=2014-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812001003/http://www.theweathernetwork.com/news/articles/iselle-makes-landfall-power-outages-and-flooding-reported/33639|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。強風還吹倒電線，造成大範圍停電，影響約23,000名電力客戶<ref name=Outage>{{cite news|title=Iselle lashes Hawaii with wind, rain as Julio threatens|author=Ken Wills|agency=Reuters|accessdate=2015-01-13|date=2014-08-08|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/08/us-usa-storm-hawaii-idUSKBN0G60XK20140808|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114005255/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/08/us-usa-storm-hawaii-idUSKBN0G60XK20140808|archive-date=2015-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。普納（{{lang|en|Puna}}）一所地熱發電廠在失去電力後釋放出有毒的[[硫化氫|硫化氫]]氣體，促使官員敦促附近地區的居民逃離<ref name=WSJLandfall>{{cite news|author1=Carlton, Jim|author2=Aronson, Sean|author3=Audi, Tamara|author4=Lazo, Alejandro|title=Hurricane Iselle Makes Landfall on Hawaii's Big Island|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/hurricane-iselle-makes-landfall-on-hawaiis-big-island-1407486969|accessdate=2014-08-08|work=The Wall Street Journal|agency=The Wall Street Journal|date=2014-08-08|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221074902/http://www.wsj.com/articles/hurricane-iselle-makes-landfall-on-hawaiis-big-island-1407486969|archive-date=2014-12-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但附近的一些居民仍有健康影響的報告<ref name=Impacts>{{cite news|author1=Fujimori, Leila|title=Groups demand answers on Puna power plant|url=http://punapono.com/tort/images/Advertiser.pdf|accessdate=2014-12-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221044604/http://punapono.com/tort/images/Advertiser.pdf|archivedate=2014-12-21}}</ref>。茂宜島[[庫拉_(夏威夷州)|庫拉]]的一家水處理廠亦因停電而關閉，使該地區的供水受限<ref name=BattersHawaii>{{cite news|title=Tropical Storm Iselle batters Hawaii with strong wind, heavy rain|url=http://www.wjla.com/articles/2014/08/iselle-makes-landfall-near-hawaii-weakens-to-tropical-storm-105888.html|accessdate=2014-08-08|agency=Associated Press, WJLA|publisher=Allbritton Communications|date=2014-08-08|location=Honolulu, Hawaii|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811005933/http://www.wjla.com/articles/2014/08/iselle-makes-landfall-near-hawaii-weakens-to-tropical-storm-105888.html|archive-date=2014-08-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。伊塞萊的強風也破壞約1,000棵咖啡樹和2,000多棵[[澳大利亚坚果|澳大利亚坚果]]樹。[[番木瓜|番木瓜]]農作物的損失最大<ref>{{cite news|author=John Burnette|date=2014-08-13|accessdate=2014-08-13|newspaper=Hawaii Tribune-Herald|title=Ag crops sustained extensive damage from Iselle|url=http://hawaiitribune-herald.com/news/local-news/ag-crops-sustained-extensive-damage-iselle|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813230956/http://hawaiitribune-herald.com/news/local-news/ag-crops-sustained-extensive-damage-iselle|archive-date=2014-08-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，全州約有60％的農作物遭到破壞<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Office of Senator Mazie Hirono|date=2014-09-04|accessdate=2014-09-08|title=Hirono Applauds Disaster Declaration to Help Hawaii Farmers|url=http://www.hirono.senate.gov/press-releases/hirono-applauds-disaster-declaration-to-help-hawaii-farmers|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908223947/http://www.hirono.senate.gov/press-releases/hirono-applauds-disaster-declaration-to-help-hawaii-farmers|archive-date=2014-09-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，虧損達$5500萬（2014年[[美元|美元]]）<ref name="ncdc">{{cite web|publisher=National Climatic Data Center|accessdate=2016-01-18|url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/stormevents/eventdetails.jsp?id=533920|title=Event Report for Hawaii|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170511125755/https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/stormevents/eventdetails.jsp?id=533920|archive-date=2017-05-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他農作物包括咖啡、澳大利亞堅果和鮮花亦遭破壞<ref name="ncdc"/>，該州農作物的總體損失估計為6600萬美元<ref>{{cite web|work=AON Claims Journal|date=2014-09-08|accessdate=2014-09-08|title=Economic Losses from August Quake, Weather in U.S. Top $4 Billion: Aon|url=http://www.claimsjournal.com/news/national/2014/09/08/254327.htm|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908230037/http://www.claimsjournal.com/news/national/2014/09/08/254327.htm|archive-date=2014-09-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。只有一宗已知的死亡事件是由風暴直接引起——一名19歲的女子在已封閉的州立公園遠足時被洪水沖走<ref>{{cite web|author=Valdes, Manuel|title=How Tropical Weather Shook up an Island Paradise |url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2014/aug/10/hawaiis-big-island-struggles-after-tropical-storm/?page=all|publisher=Washington Times |accessdate=2015-01-13|date=2014-08-10}}</ref>。超過250名業主有損毀報告，至少有11所房屋被毀、28所房屋受到嚴重破壞<ref name="kpua"/>。公共損失和清除瓦礫的費用估計為1320萬美元<ref name="wht">{{cite news|newspaper=West Hawaii Today|accessdate=2014-08-27|date=2014-08-25|title=Storm drains state’s disaster fund|author=Colin M. Stewart|url=http://westhawaiitoday.com/news/local-news/storm-drains-state-s-disaster-fund|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140827105923/http://westhawaiitoday.com/news/local-news/storm-drains-state-s-disaster-fund|archive-date=2014-08-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。夏威夷州的損失總額介乎1.48億至3.25億美元之間<ref name="TCR"/>。

由於伊塞萊帶來威脅，{{link-en|夏威夷州副州長|Lieutenant Governor of Hawaii|副州長}}候選人華納·薩頓（{{lang|en|Warner Sutton}}）要求州長[[尼尔·阿伯克龙比|尼尔·阿伯克龙比]]延遲8月9日的{{link-en|2014年夏威夷州州長選舉|2014 Hawaii gubernatorial election|初選}}。不過州長拒絕這要求<ref>{{cite news|author=Keoki Kerr|title=In face of storms and a request to delay, primary election still on|agency=Hawaii News Now|date=2014-08-06|accessdate=2014-08-10|url=http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26207596/in-face-of-storms-and-a-request-to-delay-primary-election-still-on|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809010539/http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26207596/in-face-of-storms-and-a-request-to-delay-primary-election-still-on|archive-date=2014-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而初選則按計劃進行。然而，大島上兩個通往投票站的道路遭風暴破壞，促使官員透過這些地區的[[缺席投票|缺席投票]]來決定選舉<ref>{{cite news|newspaper=Hawaii News Now|date=2014-08-09|accessdate=2014-08-10|title=Storm damage forces state to postpone election for two Big Island polling places|url=http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26237677/storm-damage-forces-state-to-postpone-election-for-two-big-island-polling-places|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809182930/http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/26237677/storm-damage-forces-state-to-postpone-election-for-two-big-island-polling-places|archive-date=2014-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。現任[[美国参议院|參議員]][[布萊恩·夏茲|布萊恩·夏茲]]和[[美国众议院|女國會議員]]{{link-en|科琳·哈納布薩|Colleen Hanabusa}}之間舉行激烈的競選後，{{link-en|2014年美國參議院夏威夷州特別選舉|2014 United States Senate special election in Hawaii|參議院初選}}與州長初選同日舉行，夏茲僅領先1,635票，兩者的票數過於接近。因此，選舉取決於兩個已關閉的投票站，超過8,000人可以選擇透過郵件投票<ref>{{cite news|author=Edward-Isaac Dovere|author2=Kyle Cheney|title=Schatz-Hanabusa race too close to call|publisher=Politico|accessdate=2014-08-10|date=2014-08-10|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2014/08/hawaii-governor-race-neil-abercrombie-109885.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810182917/http://www.politico.com/story/2014/08/hawaii-governor-race-neil-abercrombie-109885.html|archive-date=2014-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來改為在8月15日親自投票，縱然哈納布薩的競選活動因風暴帶來的損失而遇到挑戰，而夏茲最終獲勝<ref>{{Cite news|author=Sean Sullivan|newspaper=The Washington Post|date=2014-08-16|accessdate=2014-08-17|title=Hawaii’s Schatz defeats Hanabusa in Senate primary|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/post-politics/wp/2014/08/16/hawaiis-sen-schatz-defeats-hanabusa-in-primary/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140816210129/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/post-politics/wp/2014/08/16/hawaiis-sen-schatz-defeats-hanabusa-in-primary/|archive-date=2014-08-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。夏威夷[[美國公民自由聯盟|美國公民自由聯盟]]後來就如何處理選舉起訴州政府<ref>{{cite news|agency=Associated Press |date=2014-08-27 |accessdate=2014-08-27 |title=Hawaii AG’s office urges primary lawsuit dismissal |newspaper=West Hawaii Today |url=http://westhawaiitoday.com/community-bulletin/hawaii-ag-s-office-urges-primary-lawsuit-dismissal-0 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140902025140/http://westhawaiitoday.com/community-bulletin/hawaii-ag-s-office-urges-primary-lawsuit-dismissal-0 |archivedate=2014-09-02 }}</ref>。

==善後及記錄==
[[File:Iselle2014filledrainblk.gif|250px]]
風暴過後，[[夏威夷電力實業|夏威夷電力實業]]致力恢復大島的電力供應，派遣卡車上道路清除樹木和碎片。截至8月20日，99％的用戶已恢復供電，但風暴過後12天仍有1,100名居民沒有電力供應<ref>{{cite news|author=Clayton Wakida|title=Power restored to 99% of HELCO customers|publisher=KITV4.com|date=2014-08-20|url=http://www.kitv.com/news/power-restored-to-99-of-helco-customers/27646482#!bG4RFU|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821160528/http://www.kitv.com/news/power-restored-to-99-of-helco-customers/27646482#!bG4RFU|archive-date=2014-08-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直到9月11日（風暴後大約五星期），才恢復所有供電<ref>{{cite news|author=Clayton Wakida |title=Hawaiian Telcom service restored on Big Island |publisher=KITV4.com |date=2014-09-11 |url=http://www.kitv.com/news/hawaiian-telcom-service-restored-on-big-island/28021256 |accessdate=2014-09-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140912070527/http://www.kitv.com/news/hawaiian-telcom-service-restored-on-big-island/28021256 |archivedate=2014-09-12 }}</ref>。風暴過後的調查顯示，伊塞萊造成的破壞主要是來自島上非原生的樹木，在強風下降低抗風功能並被吹斷<ref>{{cite news|agency=Associated Press |date=2014-08-20 |title=Officials: Invasive trees caused more storm damage |accessdate=2014-08-20 |url=http://www.kpua.net/news.php?id=30115 |publisher=Hawaii News |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821104747/http://www.kpua.net/news.php?id=30115 |archivedate=2014-08-21 }}</ref>。風暴過後，夏威夷各地的居民透過夏威夷島聯合之路（{{lang|en|Hawaii Island United Way}}）捐款以幫助受害者，共籌得超過8萬美元。當地慈善機構向3,000多個家庭派發2,300公斤的食物<ref>{{cite news|agency=Associated Press|date=2014-08-20|accessdate=2014-08-20|title=More than $80K donated for relief|publisher=The Maui News|url=http://www.mauinews.com/page/content.detail/id/588838/More-than--80K-donated-for-relief.html?nav=5031|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821122512/http://www.mauinews.com/page/content.detail/id/588838/More-than--80K-donated-for-relief.html?nav=5031|archive-date=2014-08-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[聯邦緊急事務管理署|聯邦緊急事務管理署]]在8月19日完成房屋災害調查，是宣佈進入聯邦災難的第一步。由於風暴帶來的損失，[[美国众议院|眾議院女議員]][[圖爾西·加巴德|圖爾西·加巴德]]說「我敦促聯邦緊急事務管理、夏威夷縣、州長和總統[[贝拉克·奥巴马|奧巴馬]]盡快宣布伊塞萊帶來的破壞是一場自然災害，以便普納人能夠立刻得到救助」<ref>{{Cite news|author=Colin Stewart|newspaper=West Hawaii Today|date=2014-08-20|accessdate=2014-08-20|title=FEMA finishes Puna home survey: But approval of federal relief in wake of Iselle could be more than week away|url=http://westhawaiitoday.com/hurricane-season-2014/fema-finishes-puna-home-survey-approval-federal-relief-wake-iselle-could-be|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140822022053/http://westhawaiitoday.com/hurricane-season-2014/fema-finishes-puna-home-survey-approval-federal-relief-wake-iselle-could-be|archive-date=2014-08-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。8月25日，在國家耗盡其災難基金後，州長阿伯克龍比正式要求聯邦援助<ref name="wht"/>，但由於破壞不足，聯邦緊急事務管理署拒絕其要求<ref name="kpua">{{Cite news|agency=Associated Press |date=2014-08-29 |accessdate=2014-08-29 |title=FEMA denies Hawaii's post-storm disaster request |newspaper=Hawaii News |url=http://www.kpua.net/news.php?id=30139 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903082030/http://www.kpua.net/news.php?id=30139 |archivedate=2014-09-03 }}</ref>。不過，[[美国农业部长|農業部長]][[汤姆·维尔萨克|汤姆·维尔萨克]]宣布該州出現農業災難，促使{{link-en|小企業管理局|Small Business Administration}}可向小企業發放聯邦災難貸款<ref>{{Cite news|agency=Associated Press|date=2014-09-05|accessdate=2015-01-13|title=Big Island businesses eligible for disaster loans in aftermath of Tropical Storm Iselle|publisher=Maui News|url=http://www.mauinews.com/page/content.detail/id/589416/Big-Island-businesses-eligible-for-disaster-loans.html?nav=8|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114010237/http://www.mauinews.com/page/content.detail/id/589416/Big-Island-businesses-eligible-for-disaster-loans.html?nav=8|archive-date=2015-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。聯邦緊急事務管理署的決定在9月12日獲撤銷，當時聯邦政府已批准重建公共建築，以及未來的減災措施的援助<ref>{{Cite news|agency=Associated Press |date=2014-09-15 |accessdate=2014-09-15 |title=Obama approves aid for some repairs after Iselle |newspaper=Hawaii News |url=http://www.kpua.net/news.php?id=30184 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114012655/http://www.kpua.net/news.php?id=30184 |archivedate=2015-01-14 }}</ref>。

當伊塞萊以風力時速95公里登陸大島時，它成為有史以來吹襲該島最強的熱帶氣旋，以及以熱帶風暴或更高強度吹襲該島僅有的三場風暴之一，其餘兩場分別為{{link-en|1958年太平洋颶風季|1958 Pacific hurricane season|1958年}}的第七號熱帶風暴及[[2016年太平洋颶風季|2016年]]{{link-en|颶風達比 (2016年)|Hurricane Darby (2016)|熱帶風暴達比}}。如果伊塞萊能以颶風標準登陸，那將會是大島首次遭颶風吹襲<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Accuweather|date=2014-08-09|accessdate=2014-08-10|title=Iselle Unloads Flooding Rain, Damaging Winds on Hawaii|url=http://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-news/hurricane-iselle-to-impact-haw/31586142|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809063801/http://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-news/hurricane-iselle-to-impact-haw/31586142|archive-date=2014-08-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。風暴估計損失介乎$1.48億至$3.25億之間（2014年[[美元|美元]]），伊塞萊成為[[美國|美國]][[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]第三損失最大的熱帶氣旋，即使計入通貨膨脹。對該州造成更大破壞的熱帶氣旋是{{link-en|1982年太平洋颶風季|1982 Pacific hurricane season|1982年}}[[飓风伊娃|飓风伊娃]]和[[1992年太平洋颶風季|1992年]][[颶風伊尼基|颶風伊尼基]]<ref name="Hawaii Hurricanes 1900-2010">{{cite web|publisher=National Hurricane Center|accessdate=2014-08-31|title=Deadliest & Costliest Tropical Cyclones (1900-2010) for Hawaii, Puerto Rico and the U.S. Virgin Islands (page 31)|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/nws-nhc-6.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121221124852/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/nws-nhc-6.pdf|archive-date=2012-12-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=TMCnet.com|date=2014-08-14|accessdate=2014-08-31|title=Hurricane Iselle Downs Power in Honolulu|url=http://www.tmcnet.com/channels/power-protection/articles/386592-hurricane-iselle-downs-power-honolulu.htm|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140912071217/http://www.tmcnet.com/channels/power-protection/articles/386592-hurricane-iselle-downs-power-honolulu.htm|archive-date=2014-09-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，伊塞萊是登陸夏威夷主要島嶼的第三強勁的熱帶氣旋，僅次於{{link-en|颶風黛蒂|Hurricane Dot}}和伊尼基{{refn|name="注1"|group=注|颶風伊娃並登陸夏威夷，而是以強勁一級颶風的標準正面吹襲該島嶼。}}<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Hawaii 24/7|date=2014-08-05|accessdate=2014-08-10|title=List of Hawaii hurricanes dating to 1843|url=http://www.hawaii247.com/2014/08/05/list-of-hawaii-hurricanes-dating-to-1843/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812205300/http://www.hawaii247.com/2014/08/05/list-of-hawaii-hurricanes-dating-to-1843/|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

